{
  "stem": "1338.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father always referred to Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Zeidman as an extremely honest man despite the fact that he's very religious.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it stayed with me a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, I don't think that that was-- he didn't mean that as a general statement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm sure some of his best friends-- but the point is that it kind of implied where I came from and what kind of an attitude there was to extreme religion, at least behavior.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That does not mean that my father was not traditionally-- spoke-- not spoke, because I couldn't understand him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He spoke a different pronunciation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he knew Hebrew perfectly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And his-- he was never-- we never went to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Since they lived in the country, isolated, they brought tutors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my understanding from my father was that his Hebrew tutor was the one who tutors the Rothschild.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I presume that he must have had good teachers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His Russian was excellent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Shabbat-- well, first of all remember, I was in a Hebrew high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the environment of the school must translate into home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So whether my father wanted me or not-- I remember, for example, my father at one point insisted I don't write on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He thought that, you know, you're going to a Hebrew high school and that's where you study religion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, but strangely enough he did, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I don't know what that means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't think he was not sincere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it's just that he was trying to give me the Jewish education.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He obviously was doing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he was doing it in more modern form, obviously.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was not-- so even that was not that-- he wasn't insisting on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And obviously, I did, most of the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
